<li>Which AI platforms use fan-out (and how many sub-queries they generate)</li>
<li>Why 68% of AI-cited pages do not rank in the top 10 organic results</li>
<li>How to identify the sub-queries AI generates for your target keywords</li>
<li>The "atomic answer" content structure that wins in fan-out search</li>
